Quest:Across the Spiral

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Know Your Enemy

Given By: Tala Snakesquasher

Giver Location: Stone Town
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Defeat Musuth Berserkers and

Collect 3 Headdresses

Talk to Tala Snakesquasher
Hand In: Tala Snakesquasher

Reward:

260
8,080
Ra
Skeletal Dragon
Efreet
Snow Angel
Rebirth
Medusa
Leviathan

Leads to:

Welcome to the Jungle

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Across the Spiral should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Across the Spiral in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
